  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e9620f8c34305754d8cc9a7e49e852d9, type: 3}
  m_Name: Speech_en
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Unity.Localization::UnityEngine.Localization.Tables.StringTable
  m_LocaleId:
    m_Code: en
  m_SharedData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 991c04154cea34203a64a5fe4f5e097e, type: 2}
  m_Metadata:
    m_Items: []
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 2529198236229632
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2529182356594688
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882818806898688
    m_Localized: Comfy Bed
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882819079528448
    m_Localized: The comfy bed beckons . . . .
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882819180191744
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882819276660736
    m_Localized: Hello, comfy bed.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882819377324032
    m_Localized: Comfy Bed
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882819473793024
    m_Localized: Are you sure you want to go to sleep?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882819570262016
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882819666731008
    m_Localized: Yeah
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882819763200000
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882819859668992
    m_Localized: No, I have work to do
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882819956137984
    m_Localized: Comfy Bed
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882820052606976
    m_Localized: See you next time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882820144881664
    m_Localized: Comfy Bed
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882820241350656
    m_Localized: Really?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882820337819648
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882820434288640
    m_Localized: 'On second thought . . . '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882820530757632
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882820627226624
    m_Localized: Yeah, I'm sure.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882820719501312
    m_Localized: Comfy Bed
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882820820164608
    m_Localized: You can't take this back, you know?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882820912439296
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882821008908288
    m_Localized: I know.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882821101182976
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882821197651968
    m_Localized: Wait, I didn't mean it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882821294120960
    m_Localized: Comfy Bed
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882821386395648
    m_Localized: Ok.  See you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882821487058944
    m_Localized: Comfy Bed
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2882821579333632
    m_Localized: Frankie.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884730478387200
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884730792960000
    m_Localized: Skip Root
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884730897817600
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884731002675200
    m_Localized: Oh no oh no oh no oh no.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884731107532800
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884731224973312
    m_Localized: Come on Frankie, please go find Tilly.  She'll kill me if we just
      leave her down there.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884731531157504
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884731631820800
    m_Localized: What's that?  You say you saw me at the PortaBank (TM)?  I don't
      know what you're talking about, I work here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884731732484096
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884731833147392
    m_Localized: Aside from you and Horse, I'm literally the only person who does
      work around here
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884731933810688
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884732034473984
    m_Localized: You want the key to the ballpit?  Alright, let's tango.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884732139331584
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884732239994880
    m_Localized: Thanks Frankie, I really owe ya one.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884732340658176
    m_Localized: Steve5000
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884732441321472
    m_Localized: Root Node Skipped
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884732546179072
    m_Localized: Steve5000
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884732646842368
    m_Localized: Oh, hey Francis . . . err, Frankie.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884732751699968
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884732856557568
    m_Localized: Uh . . . what the hell was that?  What ARE you?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884732957220864
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884733057884160
    m_Localized: Frankie!  I need your help, I really messed up this time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884733162741760
    m_Localized: Steve5000
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884733259210752
    m_Localized: Hey, look -- before you go in there, you should know -- the interns
      have been acting really weird.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884733359874048
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884733464731648
    m_Localized: Look, Horse locked the door to the ballpit room, but you can make
      your way down to Tilly in the basement with the elevator.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884733565394944
    m_Localized: Clever Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884733666058240
    m_Localized: After you've adventured a little, check your bank account.  You
      may be surprised to see your stocks have paid some dividends.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884734173569024
    m_Localized: Hipster
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884734274232320
    m_Localized: I think the electrical breaker tripped and needs to be reset, but
      it's in the basement and the workers here have kinda gone mad.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884734580416512
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884734685274112
    m_Localized: I dared Tilly to hop down the fireman's pole in the ballpit room
      and SHE DID.  Now she's trapped with the interns.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884734790131712
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884734890795008
    m_Localized: Root
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884734991458304
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884735092121600
    m_Localized: I got these neat refurbished portable sheds on discount!  Can you
      believe it?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884735192784896
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884735297642496
    m_Localized: Oh, did you want me to save your progress so far?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884735402500096
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884735503163392
    m_Localized: Sure!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884735608020992
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884735708684288
    m_Localized: Nah, not today
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884736216195072
    m_Localized: L'il Slugger
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884736316858368
    m_Localized: What?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884736421715968
    m_Localized: L'il Slugger
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884736518184960
    m_Localized: So what?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884736623042560
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884736719511552
    m_Localized: Oh, uh, hi Tilly.  Good to uh . . . see you again . . . in good
      spirits.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884736824369152
    m_Localized: L'il Slugger
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884736925032448
    m_Localized: Friggin' nerd!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884737231216640
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884737331879936
    m_Localized: Wait!  Don't hurt me, I'm not your average Vole!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884737843585024
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884737948442624
    m_Localized: So study up before your fights -- you can see what you can do by
      pressing Tab and selecting Abilities.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884738049105920
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884738149769216
    m_Localized: In battle, select which ability you want with your "W-A-S-D" keys
      and then lock it in with "E".
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884738250432512
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884738346901504
    m_Localized: Watch out for the interns, they're really riled up about something.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884738451759104
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884738552422400
    m_Localized: This is the last sentence I memorized.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884738653085696
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884738753748992
    m_Localized: Squeak.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884738854412288
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884738963464192
    m_Localized: Root
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884739882016768
    m_Localized: Skilled Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884739982680064
    m_Localized: '*thwrp* Don''t get too close. *pfft*'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884740288864256
    m_Localized: Skilled Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884740389527552
    m_Localized: '*pbbbt* Maybe the chili last night was a bad idea. *poot*'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884741178056704
    m_Localized: Pretty Girl
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884741282914304
    m_Localized: Wow!  You actually made it through the forest?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884741790425088
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884741891088384
    m_Localized: '*cough* *hrkkk* Well . . . '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884742818029568
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884742918692864
    m_Localized: 'Oh, I almost forgot -- my dying words:'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884743224877056
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884743325540352
    m_Localized: Oh my go-
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884743430397952
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884743531061248
    m_Localized: The answer lies in your own memories.  You must go on a journey
      in search of your 10 curios of power to unlock the truth.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884743635918848
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884743736582144
    m_Localized: You'll meet many friends along the way.  Trust in them, rely on
      them.  You need their help to make it through this.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884743841439744
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884743942103040
    m_Localized: Go now.  Your first curio, I sense that it is close.  Somewhere
      in the nearby suburb of Prim.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884744046960640
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884744151818240
    m_Localized: The subway should take you there.  Wait, you should know this, you
      live in Prim, DON'T YOU?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884744256675840
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884744361533440
    m_Localized: Oh man, oh boy, I see the light.  This is really it now.  Before
      I go, did you listen closely enough, or do you want me to repeat this?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884744466391040
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884744567054336
    m_Localized: Yes
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884744671911936
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884744776769536
    m_Localized: No
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884744877432832
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884744978096128
    m_Localized: Oh . . . really?  Honestly, I'm barely holding on here.  Ok, I guess,
      here goes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884745095536640
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884745200394240
    m_Localized: Alright.  Well, you're a smart, capable, and brave man, Frankie. 
      Remember that.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884745301057536
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884745401720832
    m_Localized: I'm glad I got to meet you.  *squish* *slurp* *bye*
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884745506578432
    m_Localized: Default
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884745607241728
    m_Localized: Default Text to Overwrite
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884745712099328
    m_Localized: Fancy Lady
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884745812762624
    m_Localized: Is that boy still hanging around my house?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884745921814528
    m_Localized: Fancy Lady
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884746022477824
    m_Localized: I'm his mom, but to be honest, I wish he'd just leave me alone
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884746123141120
    m_Localized: Fancy Lady
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884746227998720
    m_Localized: What a bother
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884746945224704
    m_Localized: Some Guy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884747050082304
    m_Localized: Don't let the voles into your house
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884748182544384
    m_Localized: Default
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884748287401984
    m_Localized: Root Node Skipped
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884748392259584
    m_Localized: Hipster Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884748497117184
    m_Localized: Hey, I need you to present to the SVP on this issue in 10 minutes!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884748597780480
    m_Localized: Hipster Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884748702638080
    m_Localized: Cool presentation, let's do this again some time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884749013016576
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884749117874176
    m_Localized: Erk!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884749218537472
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884749323395072
    m_Localized: Unhuh.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884749424058368
    m_Localized: Hipster Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884749528915968
    m_Localized: Oh great, you have Tilly with you, let's see what you got.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884749629579264
    m_Localized: Hipster Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884749734436864
    m_Localized: Wait, where's Tilly?  Go get Tilly first!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884749839294464
    m_Localized: Hipster Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884749944152064
    m_Localized: That's the attitude!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884750049009664
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884750153867264
    m_Localized: Default Text to Overwrite
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884750258724864
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884750363582464
    m_Localized: Let me guess, Horse asked you to come down here for his *ahem* documents?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884750468440064
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884750573297664
    m_Localized: I guess it can get pretty lonely down here sometimes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884750673960960
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884750778818560
    m_Localized: Here -- I think this is what he wants.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884750879481856
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884750984339456
    m_Localized: Oh.  How did you get down here?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884751294717952
    m_Localized: Skilled Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884751399575552
    m_Localized: 'Didja fart?  . . . '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884751504433152
    m_Localized: Skilled Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884751605096448
    m_Localized: . . .
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884751915474944
    m_Localized: Skilled Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884752020332544
    m_Localized: '*SNORT* By the way, Horse is in a really bad mood *HYUK*.  He probably
      won''t even talk to you if you aren''t carrying Hay.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884752120995840
    m_Localized: Skilled Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884752225853440
    m_Localized: '*HYUK* Got some Hay on ya?  Well done.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884752326516736
    m_Localized: Skilled Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884752435568640
    m_Localized: Spankety spankety.  *SNORT*  Now get.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884753786134528
    m_Localized: Tilly
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884753890992128
    m_Localized: Yes?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884755228975104
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884755329638400
    m_Localized: Keep an eye on the STATUS EFFECTS being applied to your character. 
      Use a RESTORATIVE SKILL or ITEM if you need.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884755434496000
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884755539353600
    m_Localized: Team work is the dream work, am I right?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884755849732096
    m_Localized: Phil Too
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884755954589696
    m_Localized: Root Node Skipped
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884756055252992
    m_Localized: Phil Too
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884756168499200
    m_Localized: Your vibe is pretty gnarled isn't it?  Try improving your Beauty,
      Frankie!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884756273356800
    m_Localized: Phil Too
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884756382408704
    m_Localized: Lookin' fly!  Let me vibe with you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884756487266304
    m_Localized: Phil Too
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884756592123904
    m_Localized: 'I''m going to tell you this since you don''t already know:  pay
      attention to your stats!  '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884756705370112
    m_Localized: Phil Too
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884756827004928
    m_Localized: As you your stat values increase, you might unlock new abilities. 
      I bet you have a new ability to check out right now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884756944445440
    m_Localized: Phil Too
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884757070274560
    m_Localized: Alright, let's get goin'.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884758827687936
    m_Localized: Default
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884758949322752
    m_Localized: Default Text to Overwrite
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884759293255680
    m_Localized: Hipster Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884759402307584
    m_Localized: I remember what I needed to tell you now, but it wasn't that important.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884759742046208
    m_Localized: Hipster Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884759851098112
    m_Localized: Uh.  Hmmm...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884761851781120
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884761952444416
    m_Localized: No, you'-
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884762904551424
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884763005214720
    m_Localized: '*sluuuuurp* *chomp* *toss*'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884763319787520
    m_Localized: Porta Attendant
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884763424645120
    m_Localized: HI!  Welcome to PortaBank (TM)!  Your number one portable banking
      solution!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884763542085632
    m_Localized: Porta Attendant
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884763646943232
    m_Localized: Let me know if you have any questions!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884765018480640
    m_Localized: Lucy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884765123338240
    m_Localized: Root Node to Skip
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884765228195840
    m_Localized: Lucy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884765333053440
    m_Localized: '*Smooch* I''m so happy to see you.  You must have had a long day.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884765437911040
    m_Localized: Lucy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884765538574336
    m_Localized: Why don't you have a bite to eat and head to bed?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884765643431936
    m_Localized: Lucy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884765748289536
    m_Localized: Good morning, sleepyhead!  Are you going to head into town today?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884765857341440
    m_Localized: Lucy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884765962199040
    m_Localized: I'm thinking of getting one of those little robots to clean the
      house.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884766067056640
    m_Localized: Lucy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884766176108544
    m_Localized: What are they called again?  Vwoomba?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884766280966144
    m_Localized: Lucy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884766385823744
    m_Localized: I heard a cute new coffee shop opened up in town.  We should check
      it out sometime!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884766490681344
    m_Localized: Lucy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884766595538944
    m_Localized: Make sure you watch out for wild animals.  They've been straying
      closer to the paths lately.  Scary!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884766910111744
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884767014969344
    m_Localized: Mmmhmm?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884767119826944
    m_Localized: Fashionable Girl
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884767224684544
    m_Localized: Yeah, I mean, I swear this is my place
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884767329542144
    m_Localized: Fashionable Girl
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884767438594048
    m_Localized: What's it to ya anyway?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884768604610560
    m_Localized: Counting Guy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884768709468160
    m_Localized: . . . seventeen one thousand . . . wait, where was I?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884769028235264
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884769137287168
    m_Localized: Finally you've arrived.  My name is Phil, and I come bearing an
      urgent message.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884769242144768
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884769355390976
    m_Localized: Are you a talking cup of noodles?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884769460248576
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884769569300480
    m_Localized: 'I may look like a delicious cup of noodles, but I''m actually a
      sophisticated artificial intelligence.  '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884769678352384
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884769783209984
    m_Localized: Wait . . . . .
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884770315886592
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884770420744192
    m_Localized: They must be moving faster than I thought.  We need to find some
      chopsticks immediately.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884770529796096
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884770638848000
    m_Localized: Once you find the chopsticks, you need to pour some hot water onto
      me and mush my noodles around.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884770961809408
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884771066667008
    m_Localized: Errr?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884771171524608
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884771276382208
    m_Localized: Ok?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884771381239808
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884771494486016
    m_Localized: I'm sorry, but now isn't the time to explain.  Quickly!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884772664696832
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884772773748736
    m_Localized: I think they have some stocked in the convenience machines.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884774199812096
    m_Localized: Skilled Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884774304669696
    m_Localized: Root
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884775248388096
    m_Localized: Skilled Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884775353245696
    m_Localized: Ah, my back!  You totally f***ed up my back!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884775458103296
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884775562960896
    m_Localized: Default Text to Overwrite
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884776083054592
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884776187912192
    m_Localized: 'It looks like everything is back to normal.  '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884776292769792
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884776397627392
    m_Localized: And my 401k is tanking . . . *sad squeak*
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884776502484992
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884776607342592
    m_Localized: How am I ever going to support my family like this? *desperate squeak*
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884776871583744
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884776984829952
    m_Localized: Uhh
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884777093881856
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884777198739456
    m_Localized: '*squeak* I agree, Frankie.  We need to overthrow our capitalist
      overlords.  '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884777307791360
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884777412648960
    m_Localized: Erk
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884777517506560
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884777622364160
    m_Localized: Uhhh
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884777727221760
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884777836273664
    m_Localized: Thanks for giving me this great advice.  *happy squeak* You're a
      real pal.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884778155040768
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884778264092672
    m_Localized: If anyone can sort this out, it's you.  Be careful! *inspiring squeak*
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884778368950272
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884778473807872
    m_Localized: It's like nobody even noticed the power went out.  Weird.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884778582859776
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884778687717376
    m_Localized: '*spooky squeak*'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884779639824384
    m_Localized: Ron
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884779744681984
    m_Localized: Anyway, want to save your progress so far?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884780008923136
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884780113780736
    m_Localized: Nah, no thanks.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884780214444032
    m_Localized: Ron
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884780315107328
    m_Localized: Want me to shuttle you back to the PortaBank?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884780570959872
    m_Localized: Tilly
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884780671623168
    m_Localized: Nah.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884780772286464
    m_Localized: Clever Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884780877144064
    m_Localized: Can you help me out with this problem?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884780982001664
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884781082664960
    m_Localized: Okay
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884781183328256
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884781283991552
    m_Localized: No
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884781388849152
    m_Localized: Clever Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884781489512448
    m_Localized: You shouldn't spoil me too much, I'll never build up a real work
      ethic if you keep going on like this.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884781594370048
    m_Localized: Clever Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884781695033344
    m_Localized: You're right.  I really need to take care of this myself.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884781997023232
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884782101880832
    m_Localized: Hi there!  I'm not your enemy, merely a vole who wants to give you
      some advice!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884782202544128
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884782303207424
    m_Localized: In this demo you will face enemies of varying difficulty in order
      to gauge your combat prowess
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884782613585920
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884782714249216
    m_Localized: Yes, well, be warned!  Combat does not pause in Frankie!  Once an
      enemy can attack, they will!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884783020433408
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884783121096704
    m_Localized: As you gain new skills, you'll need to traverse deeper into your
      skill tree using the same directional keys.  Let's cross that bridge when we
      get there though!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884783225954304
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884783326617600
    m_Localized: Mmmm.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884783431475200
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884783532138496
    m_Localized: OK!  That's it.  That's all, did you need me to repeat these instructions?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884783636996096
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884783737659392
    m_Localized: No
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884783838322688
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884783938985984
    m_Localized: Yes
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884784240975872
    m_Localized: Beautiful Tapestry
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884784341639168
    m_Localized: Hello Francis
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884784446496768
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884784547160064
    m_Localized: Are you speaking to me?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884784849149952
    m_Localized: Beautiful Tapestry
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884784954007552
    m_Localized: Do you want to join me, Francis??
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884785054670848
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884785155334144
    m_Localized: Yes
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884785260191744
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884785360855040
    m_Localized: Of course
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884785461518336
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884785562181632
    m_Localized: Uhhh
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884785662844928
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884785763508224
    m_Localized: Yes
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884785864171520
    m_Localized: Beautiful Tapestry
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884785969029120
    m_Localized: Bald is beautiful.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884786069692416
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884786178744320
    m_Localized: Bald
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884786287796224
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884786396848128
    m_Localized: Bald is
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884786505900032
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884786610757632
    m_Localized: Bald is beautiful.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884787160211456
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884787260874752
    m_Localized: Oh.  Oh.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884787776774144
    m_Localized: Estelle
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884787877437440
    m_Localized: 'Hey, if you find yourself with a new piece for your outfit . .
      . '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884788384948224
    m_Localized: Default
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884788485611520
    m_Localized: Errr?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884788586274816
    m_Localized: Estelle
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884788686938112
    m_Localized: Oh, you're really fresh aren't you.  Access player menus by pressing
      the `TAB` key.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884788791795712
    m_Localized: Comfy Bed
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884788896653312
    m_Localized: Hello again, Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884788997316608
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884789097979904
    m_Localized: Hello, comfy bed
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884789202837504
    m_Localized: Comfy Bed
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884789303500800
    m_Localized: Shall we?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884789408358400
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884789509021696
    m_Localized: Yes please
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884790020726784
    m_Localized: Clever Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884790125584384
    m_Localized: Hngh.  You really got me.  Alright, here's my secret.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884790431768576
    m_Localized: Clever Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884790532431872
    m_Localized: There's a PortaBank (TM) just outside this very office building.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2884791450984448
    m_Localized: Tilly
    m_Metadata:
